text: Mohammad A. Akim is a Jatiya Party politician and the former Member of Parliament of Comilla-7. ==Career== Akim was elected to parliament from Comilla-7 as a Jatiya Party candidate in 1986. ==References== Category:Jatiya Party politicians Category:Living people Category:3rd Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Mohammad A. Akim
